<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef81a3e0-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2329"><num value="2329">§ 2329.</num><heading> Register of protected plant varieties</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall maintain a register of descriptions of United States protected plant varieties.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef81a3e1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/91/577/tI/s9">Pub. L. 91–577, title I, § 9</ref>, <date date="1970-12-24">Dec. 24, 1970</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1543">84 Stat. 1543</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/96/574/s4">Pub. L. 96–574, § 4</ref>, <date date="1980-12-22">Dec. 22, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/3350">94 Stat. 3350</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idef81a3e2-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idef81a3e3-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idef81a3e4-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1980—<ref href="/us/pl/96/574">Pub. L. 96–574</ref> substituted “descriptions” for “published specifications”, and struck out provisions requiring maintenance of a file for other information.</p>
</note>
